metadata.name: GOLDEN HARE
metadata.description:
Sami contacted me late one evening and asked if I wanted to swing by and photograph her in a gold bunny mask. Sami styled a photoshoot earlier in the day and had purchased a mask which was never used. I've not seen Sami in some time, so it was easy for me to say "yes". 
Golden Hare is one of a few images we shot that night on 35mm film and will be the first of 1 of one's in The Velveteen Collection to be released, with my PFP source image, "Bad Bunny", to be the last.
A museum quality framed print will be awarded to the collector for any sale exceeding 1eth. Overseas shipping to be paid by the recipient.
10% of the sales with be going back to Sami.
Not for commercial use.
